Derived code and attribution
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

mbus is part of the *mpump* family of local-first browser instruments by the
same author. All sibling projects are licensed AGPL-3.0-or-later, and the code
reused here is reused under AGPL-3.0-or-later with attribution within the same
author and suite. The following portions are derived from sibling projects:

* Build tooling, the PWA service worker + precache strategy, and the
  Vite / TypeScript / ESLint configuration patterns — derived from **mkeys**
  (vite.config.ts precache manifest plugin, public/sw.js, the tsconfig split,
  eslint.config.js, and the theme-token / global-CSS structure).

* The README structure (badges, ASCII architecture diagram, scripts table,
  manual QA checklist, repository map, Family section) follows the shared
  m-suite README template, of which **mkeys** is the current reference.

* The pure 16-bit PCM WAV encoder (src/patchbay/wav.ts) is adapted from
  **mtape** (src/recording/wav.ts), trimmed to the 16-bit case for the
  monitor capture.

The mbus-client library (packages/mbus-client) is original to this repository
(built in phase 1) and is the seed of a future shared `mcore`; the app consumes
its public API unmodified.

These derivations were confirmed by the suite lead. Because every source project
is AGPL-3.0-or-later by the same author, the reuse is covered by that license;
this NOTICE records the lineage for attribution and transparency.
